name: Angel Cove (Main Fork)
description:
Introduction

This is the exit for South Fork. Permanent landlines are in place in 3 drops to aid in ascending. The exit up North Fork is used and maintained regularly by BASE jumpers. All can be up-climber except one without a handline. South Fork is the technical fork of Angel Cove. Descending South Fork and exiting up North Fork is the recommended route for technical canyoneers.
